ques.p: To ask the Secretary of State for Justice how many probation service employees of each grade there were in probation areas on 31 December (a) 2006, (b) 2007, (c) 2008 and (d) 2009; and if he will make a statement.

reply.p: The staff in post figures for the probation service by job group at 31 December 2006-2009 are shown in the following table.
The table shows that there was an overall decrease in staff in post over the period of 1,339.26 FTE (down 6.3%).
